			<div class="seven columns">
				<p>Harvest Profit is a software company in Fargo, ND. Their products include a mobile app, consulting services, and a subscription-based web app.</p>
				<p>My work with Harvest Profit was focused on improving the way their software worked. I did this by creating a comprehensive style guide and reworking functionality with users in mind. Here are some highlights from my time working with them.</p>
				<hr>
			</div>
