			</div>
			<div class="seven columns">
				<p>Customers were unsure where to start with our software. This guide was created to address that by helping our users get started. It contains easy to follow instructions describing how they can enter the needed information to get started with the software.</p>
				<p>The guide was printed and sent to customers while we worked on an onboarding flow. You can see the full guide <a href="pdf/welcome.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	
